_comment: Editing this file manually is not advised. If you'd like to change the dimensions of an act, consider consulting ekun.

entities.text:
Press jump while holding down
to drop through platforms.

While spikes are instant death,
you can walk by them just fine.

After a learning a spell,
cast it by holding @SK.

Release @SK when the spell
 is fully charged.

To quickly swap weapons or 
 skills, hold @SW and press the
 corresponding action.

Try walking slowly 
 off this ledge to
 safely swing over it.

Hold down and press jump
to release the ledge and
safely drop down below.

Try equipping your new weapon
 in your menu.

You can cycle to the inventory
 tab with either @SW or @EX

Rest at bonfires to 
heal and level up.

You can equip a melee weapon and
 ranged weapon at the same time.

You can learn new spells by
 finding and reading spellbooks
 like this one.

Walk about a shop counter and
press @EX to start shopping.

Press @SW or @EX to cycle
to the level up tab.

Try spending your new
level up point.

Grab onto this ladder 
by holding up while in
the air.

The longer you hold jump, 
 the higher you'll go.

Release ladders at any 
time by pressing jump.

You can grab onto
ledges by moving
into them while in
the air.
